Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.28,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつからかな不思議
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.62,0:02:27.79,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,この胸の奥は 君の欠片ばかり
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.33,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you Do you trust me? Someday…please say Yes
